可以使用循环来计算并累加每一项的值，最后得到结果s。以下是使用c语言编写的示例代码：

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int n;
    printf("Enter a value for n: ");
    scanf("%d", &n);

    double s = 0.0;
    int sign = 1;

    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
        s += (double) sign / i;
        sign = -sign;
    }

    printf("The value of s is: %lf\n", s);

    return 0;
}
```

示例输出：
```
Enter a value for n: 5
The value of s is: 0.783333
```

